@startuml
title Ocean View Resort - Sequence Diagram (Staff Reservation and Billing Flow)

' A4 landscape-oriented layout tuning
scale max 1600 width
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam maxMessageSize 90
skinparam ParticipantPadding 18
skinparam BoxPadding 8
skinparam ArrowThickness 1
hide footbox

actor Staff
boundary "Staff Reservation Page\n(staff/reservations.jsp)" as ResUI
control "StaffReservationServlet" as ResController
control "ReservationService" as ReservationService
entity "GuestProfileDAO" as GuestDAO
entity "RoomDAO" as RoomDAO
entity "ReservationDAO" as ReservationDAO
database "MySQL" as DB

boundary "Staff Billing Page\n(staff/billing.jsp)" as BillUI
control "StaffBillingServlet" as BillController
control "BillingService" as BillingService
entity "BillDAO" as BillDAO

== Create Reservation ==
Staff -> ResUI: Fill reservation form and submit
ResUI -> ResController: POST /staff/reservations\n(action=create, guestId, roomId, dates, guests)

ResController -> GuestDAO: findById(guestId)
GuestDAO -> DB: SELECT guest profile
DB --> GuestDAO: guest row
GuestDAO --> ResController: guest exists

ResController -> RoomDAO: findById(roomId)
RoomDAO -> DB: SELECT room
DB --> RoomDAO: room row
RoomDAO --> ResController: room exists

ResController -> ReservationService: validateForCreateOrUpdate(...)
ReservationService --> ResController: validation passed

ResController -> ReservationDAO: existsOverlappingReservation(roomId, checkIn, checkOut, null)
ReservationDAO -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) overlap check
DB --> ReservationDAO: overlap count
ReservationDAO --> ResController: overlap result

alt Overlap found
  ResController -> ResUI: Redirect with error message
else No overlap
  ResController -> ReservationDAO: create(reservation)
  ReservationDAO -> DB: INSERT reservation
  DB --> ReservationDAO: created id
  ReservationDAO --> ResController: success
  ResController -> ResUI: Redirect with success message
end

== Check-In Flow ==
Staff -> ResUI: Click check-in for reservation
ResUI -> ResController: POST /staff/reservations\n(action=checkin, id)

ResController -> ReservationDAO: findById(id)
ReservationDAO -> DB: SELECT reservation
DB --> ReservationDAO: reservation row
ReservationDAO --> ResController: reservation

ResController -> ReservationService: ensureCheckInAllowed(currentStatus)
ReservationService --> ResController: allowed

ResController -> ReservationDAO: update(status=CHECKED_IN)
ReservationDAO -> DB: UPDATE reservations
DB --> ReservationDAO: updated

ResController -> RoomDAO: update(room.status=OCCUPIED)
RoomDAO -> DB: UPDATE rooms
DB --> RoomDAO: updated

ResController -> ResUI: Redirect with success message

== Generate Bill ==
Staff -> BillUI: Fill billing form and submit
BillUI -> BillController: POST /staff/billing\n(action=create, reservationId, subtotal, tax, discount, status)

BillController -> ReservationDAO: findById(reservationId)
ReservationDAO -> DB: SELECT reservation
DB --> ReservationDAO: reservation row
ReservationDAO --> BillController: reservation exists

BillController -> BillingService: validateForCreateOrUpdate(...)
BillingService --> BillController: validation passed

BillController -> BillingService: calculateTotal(subtotal, tax, discount)
BillingService --> BillController: total

BillController -> BillDAO: create(bill)
BillDAO -> DB: INSERT bill
DB --> BillDAO: created id
BillDAO --> BillController: success

BillController -> BillUI: Redirect with success message

@enduml
